Package: lumina-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libluminautils1, lumina-desktop
Replaces: lumina-core (<< 0.8.3.372)
Description: Data files for the lumina Desktop environment
 This package provides
  * Lumina Wallpapers
  * Lumina Themes
  * Lumina Translations
  * Lumina Sounds
  * Fallback fluxbox configuration
